    <item>
      <title>MinimalWall</title>
      <link>https://ioerr.github.io/posts/minimalwall/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Sep 2010 10:09:40 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ioerr.github.io/posts/minimalwall/</guid>
      <description>你信奉“保持简单”的信条并且时时事事遵循吗？那么 MinimalWall 应该合你的胃口。 它的目的就是设计简洁至极的桌面背景图，让纷繁复杂的桌面背景精简到只剩下舒适</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>你信奉“保持简单”的信条并且时时事事遵循吗？那么<br>
<a href="http://www.minimalwall.com/">MinimalWall</a> 应该合你的胃口。<br>
它的目的就是设计简洁至极的桌面背景图，让纷繁复杂的桌面背景精简到只剩下舒适的单色、简短醒目的文字和图案。</p>
<p>想法非常不错，设计出来的壁纸也挺出色的，但我体内的恶趣味之魂又在燃烧了，所以自己也来做几张吧（为了能够实际使用，还是有所保留的）。<br>
没有装多少中文字体，大部分用的微软雅黑。</p>
<p><a href="http://s111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/?action=view&amp;current=panic.png"><img loading="lazy" src="http://i111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/panic.png" alt="Photobucket"  />
</a></p>
<p><a href="http://s111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/?action=view&amp;current=0093acb9.png"><img loading="lazy" src="http://i111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/0093acb9.png" alt="Photobucket"  />
</a></p>
<p><a href="http://s111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/?action=view&amp;current=17c23d3e.png"><img loading="lazy" src="http://i111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/17c23d3e.png" alt="Photobucket"  />
</a></p>
<p><a href="http://s111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/?action=view&amp;current=teamwork.png"><img loading="lazy" src="http://i111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/teamwork.png" alt="Photobucket"  />
</a></p>
<p><a href="http://s111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/?action=view&amp;current=42.png"><img loading="lazy" src="http://i111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/42.png" alt="Photobucket"  />
</a></p>
<p><a href="http://s111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/?action=view&amp;current=2.png"><img loading="lazy" src="http://i111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/2.png" alt="Photobucket"  />
</a></p>
<p><a href="http://s111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/?action=view&amp;current=d40c712e.png"><img loading="lazy" src="http://i111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaperSmall/d40c712e.png" alt="Photobucket"  />
</a></p>
<p>一共有30多张，就不全部放出来了，只有1024×768分辨率的，要更大的图片请自己改<br>
AI 文件。<br>
<a href="http://www.box.net/shared/vyvgq7yk85">Illustrator 文件和大图打包下载</a><br>
<a href="http://s111.photobucket.com/albums/n154/calon_plus/MinimalWallpaper/">大图相册</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
